Destination-based mapping expressed by this annotation._

_For STOMP over WebSocket messages: this is the destination of the STOMP message_(e.g. "/positions"). Ant-style path patterns (e.g. "/price.stock.*") are supported_and so are path template variables (e.g. "/price.stock.{ticker}"").
